MSnbase has been accepted into the Bioconductor project.
All source code it now hosted on the Bioc svn server [1]
and the package can be installed from within R (>= 2.13) 
with:
> source("http://www.bioconductor.org/biocLite.R")
> biocLite("MSnbase")

[1] https://hedgehog.fhcrc.org/bioconductor/trunk/madman/Rpacks/MSnbase/
